### Reading steps
- Find a book to read and click to see details
- Read synopsis and see other important informations
- Click to rent
- Select how many time he want to rent
- Pay using payment gateway
- When paid, allow to read and show in bookcase page during rent period

## Auction
- Books is a luxury item, so instead to publish many copies, there is only one tokenized book and to read you just need to rent for the time you need.
- To buy, you will click in Offers in book details page and set or accept an offer
- When the owner and the buyer closed a deal, the DvP occurs.